channel.title: Port 43546 wont open!
channel.description:
PORT 43594 WONT OPEN***
Hi,
I am using a Alcatel SpeedTouch 536v6 router, my ISP is iPrimus.. I just wanna know if im doing it right, i tested with a Portchecker, and it says its not open :/ Please help with this :P If u cant, is there some way to use a different port? EDIT- In the tester i did 43546, thats a typo i tried 43594 too, its not open [IMG]http://i306.photobucket.com/albums/nn277/uchihamatty/sdfsdfsdf.jpg[/img] Cheers.
